title: Johnson's Downda Earth Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cozy family owned restaurant - as of March 2015, the only one in Helen to offer multiple vegetarian dishes, of which some may be able to be made vegan or are vegan; please inquire. Vegans please ask if smoothies can be made vegan. Serves breakfast all day. Veggie burgers, veggie hot dogs, different salads and sides are available.
